<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 12:28:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>宝马因技术问题和中国需求疲软下调2024年利润率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-trims-2024-profit-margin-deliveries-forecast-2024-09-10/</link><description>宝马周二下调了 2024 年盈利指引，指出技术问题导致汽车交付停止以及中国主要市场的需求持续低迷。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 11:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-trims-2024-profit-margin-deliveries-forecast-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>券商报告显示，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪设定了更高的年度销售目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-byd-sets-higher-annual-sales-target-brokerage-report-shows-2024-09-10/</link><description>摩根士丹利周一在一份报告中表示，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪今年的目标是销售 400 万辆汽车，建议将该公司今年早些时候设定的 2024 年销售目标上调 11%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:59:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-byd-sets-higher-annual-sales-target-brokerage-report-shows-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>印度外交部长苏杰生表示“并未对中国业务关闭”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-foreign-minister-jaishankar-says-not-closed-business-china-2024-09-10/</link><description>印度外交部长苏杰生周二在柏林表示，印度并未“对中国业务关闭”，但问题在于该国在哪些领域与北京开展业务以及以什么条件开展业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-foreign-minister-jaishankar-says-not-closed-business-china-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>葡萄牙新政府继续禁止中国5G设备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/new-portuguese-government-keep-ban-chinese-5g-equipment-2024-09-10/</link><description>一位部长表示，葡萄牙中右翼政府将保留上届政府禁止电信公司在其 5G 网络中使用中国设备的禁令，尽管这一立场的预计成本是欧洲最严厉的之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:30:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/new-portuguese-government-keep-ban-chinese-5g-equipment-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国提议与欧盟谈判解决电动汽车关税争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-proposes-negotiations-with-eu-resolve-electric-vehicle-tariff-dispute-2024-09-10/</link><description>中国再次提出与欧盟委员会就解决经济和贸易摩擦进行谈判，以试图缓解即将对中国制造的电动汽车征收的惩罚性关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-proposes-negotiations-with-eu-resolve-electric-vehicle-tariff-dispute-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴股价因加入内地股市互联互通计划而上涨 4%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-shares-jump-4-its-addition-mainland-stock-connect-scheme-2024-09-10/</link><description>电子商务巨头阿里巴巴集团上个月将香港上市升级为主要地位，投资者对其在中国内地证券交易所上市表示欢迎，周二该股股价上涨 4.2%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-shares-jump-4-its-addition-mainland-stock-connect-scheme-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞标：电视辩论关注，中国焦虑，平静回归</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-10/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 10:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯与中国合作启动大型海军演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-teams-up-with-china-start-big-naval-drills-2024-09-10/</link><description>俄罗斯和中国军舰周二开始演习，这是莫斯科所说的一系列从地中海延伸到太平洋的大型海军演习的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 09:28:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-teams-up-with-china-start-big-naval-drills-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国对43名足球运动员和官员进行终身禁赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-bans-43-soccer-players-officials-life-match-fixing-2024-09-10/</link><description>作为打击中国最受欢迎的体育运动之一的腐败行为的一部分，中国足协对假球和赌博行为进行了为期两年的调查，对 38 名足球运动员和 5 名俱乐部官员进行了终身禁赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 09:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-bans-43-soccer-players-officials-life-match-fixing-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国和挪威将每两年举行一次绿色转型谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-norway-set-up-green-transition-talks-every-two-years-state-media-says-2024-09-10/</link><description>中国官方媒体周二称，中国和挪威同意每两年举行一次绿色转型谈判。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 08:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-norway-set-up-green-transition-talks-every-two-years-state-media-says-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯和中国舰艇在日本海举行联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-hinese-ships-meet-joint-drills-sea-japan-2024-09-10/</link><description>俄新社援引俄罗斯国防部的消息称，俄罗斯和中国海军舰艇周二在日本海举行联合演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 08:05:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-hinese-ships-meet-joint-drills-sea-japan-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将削减对特斯拉和其他中国电动汽车的拟议关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-lower-proposed-tariffs-tesla-other-evs-china-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-10/</link><description>一位知情人士周二表示，欧盟将在考虑特斯拉提交的申请后，降低对特斯拉的拟议最终关税，并小幅下调对来自中国的其他电动汽车的关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 08:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-lower-proposed-tariffs-tesla-other-evs-china-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国抨击美国针对生物技术公司的法案具有“歧视性”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/china-slams-us-bill-targeting-biotech-firms-discriminatory-2024-09-10/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，美国通过一项旨在限制与药明康德、华大基因和其他生物技术公司开展业务的法案是对中国企业的“歧视”措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 07:33:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/china-slams-us-bill-targeting-biotech-firms-discriminatory-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国接近高峰，东南亚预计将促进煤炭贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/southeast-asia-expected-boost-coal-trade-china-approaches-peak-2024-09-10/</link><description>行业官员表示，尽管最大消费国中国的需求已接近顶峰，越南和菲律宾等东南亚国家预计将在本十年内促进煤炭贸易和消费。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 07:16:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/southeast-asia-expected-boost-coal-trade-china-approaches-peak-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>六十个国家认可人工智能在军事中使用的“蓝图”；中国选择退出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/south-korea-summit-announces-blueprint-using-ai-military-2024-09-10/</link><description>周二，包括美国在内的约 60 个国家签署了一份“行动蓝图”，以管理军队中负责任地使用人工智能 (AI)，但中国是不支持这份不具法律约束力的文件的国家之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 07:02:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/south-korea-summit-announces-blueprint-using-ai-military-2024-09-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>